title: In blow to India, pro-China candidate wins Maldives election
description: President-elect Mohamed Muizzu campaigned on an “India Out” platform, pledging to expel all Indian soldiers from the archipelagic nation.

title: Kyiv downplays lack of Ukraine aid in new U.S. spending bill
description: Ukrainian officials said they were confident that bipartisan support would keep U.S. aid flowing. But others saw the move to exclude Ukraine funding as a worrying sign.

title: Police think a landfill holds women’s bodies. Why won’t they search it?
description: Manitoba’s premier says a search would cost millions of dollars while posing risks. The families of two Indigenous women who disappeared last year want action.

title: Ukraine live briefing: Congress passes funding bill without Ukraine aid to avert government shutdown
description: Proposed aid to Ukraine did not make it into the bill, but a bipartisan group of Senate leaders pledged to pursue funding for Kyiv in a separate measure.
